"title": "1265: hand of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1265",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A figure of speech which points to God's sovereign power in creation and in his actions on his people's behalf, especially in redemption. Also used as a symbol of authority and in taking oaths.</p>\n<h2>God creates by his hand</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:50\">ACT 7:50</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:2\">ISA 66:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:3\">JOB 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:8\">JOB 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:3\">PSA 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">PSA 19:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:5\">PSA 95:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:8\">PSA 138:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:13\">ISA 48:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8\">ISA 64:8</a></p>\n<h2>God holds the world in his hand</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:4\">PSA 95:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:10\">JOB 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:13\">JOB 26:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:32\">JOB 36:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:15\">PSA 31:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:12\">ISA 40:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:19–41:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's creatures are fed from his hand</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:16\">PSA 145:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:28\">PSA 104:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:17\">ISA 34:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's hand symbolises his power</h2>\n<h3>God's hand is mighty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:4\">HAB 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:15-Ps118:16\">PSA 118:15–118:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:6\">JER 18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:35\">DAN 4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:2\">AMO 9:2</a></p>\n<h3>God executes judgment by the power of his hand</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6-Amos1:8\">AMO 1:6–1:8</a></strong> <em>Judgment on the Philistine cities.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:41\">DEU 32:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:6-1Sam5:9\">1SA 5:6–5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:2\">ISA 40:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:6\">JER 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:3\">LAM 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:14\">EZK 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:4\">ZEP 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:11\">ACT 13:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand holds a cup of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:15-Jer25:17\">JER 25:15–25:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:8\">PSA 75:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:17\">ISA 51:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:16\">HAB 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand brings trouble</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:21\">JOB 19:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:13\">RUT 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:3\">1SA 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:11\">JOB 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:2\">PSA 38:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:10\">PSA 39:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand causes fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:16\">ISA 19:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:11\">ISA 23:11</a></p>\n<h2>Pleas for God to use his powerful hand</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:11\">PSA 74:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:12\">PSA 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps60:5\">PSA 60:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:6\">PSA 108:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:10\">PSA 77:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:7-Ps144:8\">PSA 144:7–144:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's powerful hand used on his people's behalf</h2>\n<h3>God redeems by his powerful hand</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:7\">PSA 138:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:41-1Kgs8:42\">1KI 8:41–8:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:32\">2CH 6:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:1\">PSA 98:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:11\">ISA 11:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:21-Ezek20:22\">EZK 20:21–20:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:33-Ezek20:34\">EZK 20:33–20:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:10\">MIC 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>God redeemed Israel from Egypt by his powerful hand</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:3\">EXO 13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:19-Exod3:20\">EXO 3:19–3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:9\">EXO 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:14\">EXO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:15\">DEU 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:8\">DEU 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:10\">NEH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:21\">JER 32:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:15\">DAN 9:15</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand ensures success for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a></strong> <em>“righteous” has the sense of “victorious”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8\">PSA 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:35\">PSA 18:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:21\">PSA 89:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:6\">ISA 42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:4\">ISA 49:4</a></p>\n<h3>God's powerful hand is invincible</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:29\">JHN 10:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:10\">PSA 139:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:13\">ISA 43:13</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand protects his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:31\">EZR 8:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:22-Exod33:23\">EXO 33:22–33:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:10\">1CH 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:5\">PSA 121:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:13\">ISA 41:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:2\">ISA 49:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:16\">ISA 49:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:3\">ISA 62:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand inspires the prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:9\">JER 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:11\">ISA 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:17\">JER 15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:3\">EZK 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:14\">EZK 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:22\">EZK 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:22\">EZK 33:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1\">EZK 37:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:1\">EZK 40:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's hand fulfils his purposes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:6\">EZR 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:12\">2CH 30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:9\">EZR 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:28\">EZR 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:18\">EZR 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:18\">NEH 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:1\">PRO 21:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24\">ECC 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:1\">ISA 45:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:66\">LUK 1:66</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:21\">ACT 11:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's uplifted hand</h2>\n<h3>Signifies his taking an oath</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:15\">NEH 9:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:8\">EXO 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:30\">NUM 14:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:40\">DEU 32:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:14\">EZK 47:14</a></p>\n<h3>Signifies his power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:12\">ISA 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:17\">ISA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:21\">ISA 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:11\">ISA 26:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's right hand symbolises his authority</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55-Acts7:56\">ACT 7:55–7:56</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:1\">PSA 110:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1\">COL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:22</a></p>\n<h2>God's hand must be recognised</h2>\n<h3>God requires submission under his hand</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:6\">1PE 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:21\">ROM 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:2\">ISA 65:2</a></p>\n<h3>The works of God's hand must be acknowledged</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:5\">PSA 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:4\">PSA 92:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:5\">PSA 143:5</a></p>",
